Brookings. Sat. 9am-2pm & Sun., 10am-2pm 945 Hassett (off ad date: 10/24/2015 
945 Hassett (off 5th St. ) Estate Sale - EVERYTHING Must go! 1/2 Price Sale on some items Starts Sunday @ Noon Houseful, antique 8-pc. 1930s bedroom set, antique sleigh bed complete, antique coffee table, pedestal table, blue LazyBoy lift chair, 2 quality couches (hide-a-bed), 7-ft. tall oak bookshelves and several other bookshelves, glass-top dining table w/4 chairs, 4-pc. oak set, 2 end tables, coffee & couch table, drop-leaf oak dining table, antique hutch and gold rimmed china, lots of crystal. 80s Broyhill white 5-pc. bedroom set, large 7-ft. tall china cabinet. Cookbooks, books. gardening and misc. Every type of countertop appliance from a Masterchefs kitchen, Maytag refrigerators, GE Profile Prodigy W/D set. So much more, too much to list! Please no earlies!
